{"type": "article", "id": 49677, "title": "这个灵感来自孟菲斯运动的挂钟，也是钥匙托盘｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-28T23:16:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}, {"id": 33327, "name": "Frame"}, {"id": 47378, "name": "NERI&HU"}, {"id": 47379, "name": "STELLAR WORKS"}, {"id": 47380, "name": "Ecobirdy"}, {"id": 47381, "name": "Alvaro Diaz Hernandez"}, {"id": 21591, "name": "Anderssen & Voll"}, {"id": 47382, "name": "Emilien Jaury"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180128225326HJKYenhCQSUDw36L.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 16.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Minimal Cocktail Set by Emilien Jaury</h3><p>瑞士洛桑艺术学院的毕业生 Emilien Jaury 设计了一套鸡尾酒器具，在形似量筒的玻璃杯中嵌套了一些小的玻璃管。受吹制玻璃时需不断旋转玻璃的过程启发，他将这种旋转动作运用到了这套器具中，当酒保混合不同配料时，他们可以同时旋转大玻璃容器和小玻璃管来配置饮料。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012823062507wjmqHEVJu3F1ip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230628FYpHJC7WDzaNlwnX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230629XmLFcCpI6V0SqyrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230629xwL9lbQmu235qUKc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.533841\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230629V8Gn7WZaEDf01dFv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230630XETG8CByKv3i59fj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230630OfuBTrAcJ9HoLW5i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Five Pouf by Anderssen &amp; Voll</h3><p>挪威设计事务所 Anderssen &amp; Voll 由 Torbjørn Anderssen 和 Espen Voll 创立，他们与丹麦设计品牌 Muuto 保持着良好的合作关系。</p><p>这款 Five Pouf 是两人为其创作的新品，这是一个多功能的，易于使用的懒人沙发坐垫，舒适且充满现代感。它采用五角形形状，直线条也区别于常见的懒人沙发的随意感。在两位设计师看来，Five Pouf 不仅可以用作懒人沙发或是坐垫，也可以用来装饰任何房间内未使用的角落。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230716u1yWFcSPlC25wAmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.280000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230717zxcRjp9CI0euDPBG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801282307173sfOXFTznBwHDNUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.278000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230718r7i9LQNCknzm4Byc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.310769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Colourful Furniture For Kids by Ecobirdy</h3><p>在最近的巴黎家居装饰博览会上，安特卫普品牌 Ecobirdy 使用回收塑料玩具，为孩子们创造了一系列丰富多彩的家居，旨在培养孩子们的“可持续性意识”。这些家具全部都是用旧塑料玩具制成的，也可以回收再利用，包括一个名为 Charlie 的轻便椅子，另有一个名为 Luisa 的边桌。另有一个带有可拆卸“喙”的鸟状容器，希望能够唤起孩子们对濒临灭绝的奇异鸟的关注，一只犀牛形状的小灯也是提醒孩子们关注犀牛的生存困境。</p><p>用 Ecobirdy 的话说，他们既想通过这组作品让孩子们感受到创造力，同时也能够提高可持续性意识。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230759K6WzywDZ8RPpI5Tb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714202\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801282308008paZKxt3nkWevcBA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230758DhnvEqdyBjJTarSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230800tKjfyTak5uBQmEbx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200085\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230801cyN6oj75EuGrwSkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200085\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230803pnmQ5PRFvkGt6dB4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706007\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bund Collection by NERI&amp;HU X STELLAR WORKS</h3><p>受“外滩”这一上海过去、现在及未来的代表的启发，家具品牌 STELLAR WORKS 与如恩设计合作，带来 Bund 系列家具，将其工业发源地和繁盛的殖民历史元素相结合。曲线柔软，皮质与布料光洁，木质椅凳致敬了注入这座城市DNA留下永恒的装饰艺术风格。同时，附在椅座上的精确切割的金属部件将整个家居组合起来成为整体。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128230959hjGFiI9nD8zv5TMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231001StB6lo5CLZY9UKc8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231002InMxZmPj9hV1DR0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801282310036UN4TlXhLEjAcgem.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231006VHkud9YB3Ty1IJlP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Add by Alvaro Diaz Hernandez</h3><p>马德里室内、家具设计师 Alvaro Diaz Hernandez 设计了一款名为 Add 的杂志架，允许用户创造性地收纳书籍、杂志。</p><p>Add 是为家庭和工作空间量身定做的兼有装饰性和功能性的杂志架，它很轻巧，便于移动，用户可以在架子上张贴图片和笔记，纺织书籍、杂志、耳机和其他时尚配饰，比如围巾、手套和太阳镜等等。它采用了简单的金属结构和坚固的木质基座，共同构成了极简主义风格 的外观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231052TVmKi1IQd3N5eBS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231052ITRQxvXhBOHkJ5Uj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231052Ggcw2zu7IO4tbPBT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231053VJHf8Y79NBaGKzed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231053yQpLlaHI05Wx1dRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.983926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>WAVES CLOCK by Frame</h3><p>巴黎设计工作室 Frame，由墨西哥设计师 Taina Campos 和法国设计师 Jeremy Godel 创立，他们创作的这款名为 WAVES 的时钟，杂糅了很多种材料，有色的橡木基座也可以作为收纳容器。WAVES 时钟既可以作为挂钟使用，也可以放在桌上。据称设计师的灵感源自孟菲斯运动，结合了孟菲斯运动的图案、几何形状和鲜艳的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231125jZpgSzIye4aH7d8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801282311255AogdriNXVWIJkle.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231125oNqKby20re3aApdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231127gVJA0Ey1c4kBWnYL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180128231127Sc5tF9WMeTp6JGDA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}